{"word":"H7001 - קְטַר - qᵉṭar - ket-ar' - Doubt","slug":"H7001","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קְטַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qᵉṭar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ket-ar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Doubt"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05D8;&#x05E8; - q<sup>e</sup>t&#x0323;ar</b> - <i>ket-ar'</i><p/>(Chaldee); from a root corresponding to <a href=\"#/H7000\">H7000</a>; a <i>knot</i> (as <i>tied</i> up), that is, (figuratively) a <i>riddle</i>; also a <i>vertebra</i> (as if a knot): - doubt, joint."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7007\">H7007</a>, <a href=\"#/H7030\">H7030</a>"}]}